Valentine Iro, the number one indicted Nigerian on a list released by the United States Federal Bureau of Investigation, has been spotted in a video living an opulent lifestyle.In the nine-second video that has now gone viral, a man with "Val Iru" written at the back of his jersey was seen dancing with his partner while people spray them with foreign currencies.There was a carpet of dollar bills on the floor while Iro and his party guests danced on it.